{"questionId":"17557","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Stephen was invited to perform a piano recital. In preparation for the event, Stephen recorded&nbsp;the amount of time, in minutes, that he rehearsed each day for the piano recital.</p>\n<p>Stephen rehearsed for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>32</mn></math>&nbsp;days and data for all these days is displayed in the following&nbsp;box-and-whisker diagram.</p>\n<p><img style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;display:block;\" src=\"__IMG__/0aef9745909e2631961e00aa78d816123ced81fb.png\" width=\"488\" height=\"256\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Write down the median rehearsal time.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>42</mn></math>&nbsp;(minutes)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(C1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><span class=\"mjpage\">[1 mark]</span></strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"17557","referenceCode":"19N.1.SL.TZ0.T_15a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down the median rehearsal time.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.2—Histograms, CF graphs, box plots"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}